#########################
###     Kde conky    ####
#########################

Place all in your home the path should be /home/<you>/conky
For gmail edit gmail.py it is in scripts folder
For hotmail edit kd1 it is en kde folder
for updates place pacupd-sh in /etc/cron.hourly and restart cron daemon
This one comes with a startup scritp use it if you want  ^_^


